  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is to compare the efficacy and safety of defibrotide versus best supportive care
      in the prevention of hepatic veno-occlusive disease (VOD) in adult and pediatric patients
      undergoing hematopoietic stem cell transplant who are at high risk or very high risk of
      developing VOD.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
